videos.headline: Arkansas St. weaves through Cornhuskers for punt return TD
videos.description: Blaise Taylor bobbles the ball, but then recovers for a 63-yard punt return TD to give Arkansas State a 7-3 lead over Nebraska.

tracking.trackingName: NCF_One-Play (Arkansas St. weaves through Cornhuskers for punt return TD) 2017/09/02 ESHEET

videos.headline: Nebraska regains lead on kickoff return TD
videos.description: Following Arkansas State's punt return touchdown, Nebraska's JD Spielman answers back with a 99-yard kickoff return touchdown to give them a  10-7 lead.

tracking.trackingName: NCF_One-Play (Nebraska regains lead on kickoff return TD) 2017/09/02 ESHEET

videos.headline: Red Wolves respond with a TD
videos.description: Justice Hansen connects with Chris Murray for a 29-yard touchdown, giving Arkansas State a 14-10 lead on Nebraska.

tracking.trackingName: NCF_One-Play (Red Wolves respond with a TD) 2017/09/02 ESHEET

videos.headline: Nebraska reclaims lead with 44-yard TD
videos.description: Tanner Lee shows off his arm with by finding Stanley Morgan Jr. for a 44-yard touchdown, putting Nebraska ahead of Arkansas State 17-14.

tracking.trackingName: NCF_One-Play (Nebraska reclaims lead with 44-yard TD) 2017/09/02 ESHEET

videos.headline: Cornhuskers extend lead with rushing TD
videos.description: Nebraska RB Mikale Wilbon scores from seven yards out to put Nebraska up 24-14 vs. Arkansas State.

tracking.trackingName: NCF_One-Play (Cornhuskers extend lead with rushing TD) 2017/09/02 ESHEET

videos.headline: Red Wolves convert on a safety
videos.description: A missed assignment on Nebraska's O-line allows Arkansas State LB Kyle Wilson to make a big play.

tracking.trackingName: NCF_One-Play (Red Wolves convert on a safety) 2017/09/02 ESHEET

videos.headline: Arkansas State pulls closer before halftime
videos.description: The Red Wolves convert on third and goal as Justice Hansen finds Blake Mack on the play-action TD.

tracking.trackingName: NCF_One-Play (Arkansas State pulls closer before halftime) 2017/09/02 ESHEET
